  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of calcium electroporation on keloids.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The keloids wil be treated with intratumoral injection of calcium followed by
      electroporation. It is a once only treatment and the patients will be followed up for 24
      months.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
